{
  "stem": "1828.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 321.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Maybe there would've been a revolution or some kind of--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--keep them busy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father's beautiful hands were bleeding from those stones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, one of those little cushions that you have, that you do something for someone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't have a jacket for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they gave me two knitted things to wear, on-- one on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took that one and I cut it up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- somebody always had a pair of scissors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I cut out mittens out of that second jacket and doubled it up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody had a-- made a needle out of wood on these-- you know, these three-tier bunk beds, cut off an eye, stitched this together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we saw him the next time, he couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I gave him a pair of mittens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after one day of carrying stones, they were torn on one side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he had turned them around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had another day out of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it made me feel so good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I didn't have a-- a proper jacket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, the children were put into a separate compound for the day, during the day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were called upon-- it was you know, by word of mouth-- to volunteer to look after them, to occupy them during the day, and to play games with them, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, I volunteered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I knew fully well what that meant, because the stories that came to us was that the schools that arrived, that groups of children arrived, their counselors went with them in order to keep them calm and organized.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The-- whoever took care of the children ended up going into the gas with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this was your duty.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
